<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-207005">
<p>I made these the other day when I was sitting around the house bored and craving something sweet. Fortunately I had all the ingredients on hand, because these were the BEST cookies I have had in a while! They are so mild yet you can very much taste the lemon&#8230;Just perfect! My husband and I ate them all in 2 days! Will definitely be making these again AND sharing the recipe with friends/family!</p>
<p class="reply"><a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2011/11/chewy-lemon-cookies/?replytocom=207005#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-body-207005", "207005", "respond", "20296")'>Reply</a></p>
</div>
