<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-239239">
<p>So easyyyy to make and they taste sooo good and they are soo chewey just the way I like cookies. I didnt have lemon extract so I used little over 2 tablespoons of lemon juice. SO GOOOOOODDDD<br />
Love your web page and your recipes.</p>
